<title>包钢板材厂爆炸致2人死亡5人失联66人送医</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E5%8C%85%E9%92%A2%E6%9D%BF%E6%9D%90%E5%8E%82%E7%88%86%E7%82%B8%E8%87%B42%E4%BA%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A15%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%81%9466%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E5%8C%BB</link>
